  Description:	If no dependent records exist for the payeeID passed 
				   in then the payee record is deleted from the payee 
				   table and the payee_change_history table is updated.

  Resources: 	dbo.admin_udfPayeeHasDependents(e.payeeid) 
				   payee
				   payee_change_history
  ------------------------------------------------------------------
  Accepts:		@PayeeID		char(12),
				   @user_type		tinyint,
				   @change_reason	char(255)

  Returns:		@Status	(0 if successful, -1 if error occurred during delete, 
							   -100 if dependent data exists)
   ==================================================================
