  Stored Procedure Name: RecPmtCancel

  Description: 	

  Resources: 	Recurring_Payment
                        User_Payee
                        Recurring_Payment_Change_History
                        Payment_History
  ------------------------------------------------------------------
  Accepts:		@recpmtid		char(10),
                     @user_type		tinyint,
                     @change_reason	char(255),
                     @canceldate datetime = '01/01/1900 00:00:00'	-- optional, default to current KKS 13July1999

  Returns:		
   ==================================================================
   Created:  	?
   By:    		?
  ------------------------------------------------------------------
  Modifications: 
	06/15/06 GNordstrom  Added this header and added an ouput clause to 
	                                          the update statement and removed "exec AddChangeHistory".
	01/26/07 GNordstrom  Added insert of Recurring_Payment.NextDueDate to DueDate field 
	                                          in PaymentHistory table and into Recurring_Payment_Change_History
	                                          table.  Also added insert of blank to MemberEmail field in 
	                                          PaymentHistory table.
	08/31/07  GNordstrom Added insert of Recurring_Payment.TrsfSource field to the
	                                          same field in the Recurring_Payment_Change_History table 
	                                          and the PaymentHistory table.
    06/18/09  GNordstrom Added new field, ProcessDay, to OUTPUT statement.   Also 
                                             changed 'INSERTED' to 'DELETED' in OUTPUT statement because 
                                             that is what it should be.  The data that is being placed into the 
                                             change history table is the same with either statement because 
                                             this is output on an update statment and the fields that were set
                                             to inserted were not being updated in the statement so the inserted
                                             is the same as the deleted for those fields.
    5/20/2012   HLiou	   Added EntryDate to payment history table
    4/28/2013   HLiou	   Added Delivery Date to payment history
    12/10/2013  HLiou	   Added Provider ID in payment history as provider sent for specific payment

